(43, 21, 21, 42, 13, 23, 24, 'what shall this man do', 'Concern for Others'' Salvation', 'This connection highlights the concern for the fate of others in relation to one''s own spiritual journey. In both passages, the question of what others will do or experience is raised, emphasizing the importance of striving for salvation.', 'theme', 0.34199999999999997, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
