(43, 21, 21, 44, 1, 6, 7, 'what shall this man do', 'Inquiry About Future Events', 'This connection highlights the disciples'' curiosity about future events. In both passages, Peter and the other disciples ask Jesus about what will happen next, reflecting their desire to understand God''s plan.', 'theme', 0.321, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
